"turned aside,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(IDrd, O, K,) from the right course or direction, (IDrd, O,) and from the road; as also"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "zAg", "text_ar": "زاغ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", aor."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "yaziygu", "text_ar": "يَزِيغُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "zayogN", "text_ar": "زَيْغٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", which latter is the more chaste: (O, TA:) the former is a dial. var. of the latter. (Msb in art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "zyg", "text_ar": "زيغ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ".) ―         -b2-  And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "zAg fiY AlmanoTiqi", "text_ar": "زاغ فِى المَنْطِقِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (Yz, O, K,) aor."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "yazuwgu", "text_ar": "يَزُوغُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (Yz, O,) inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "zawagaAnN", "text_ar": "زَوَغَانٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ","}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He declined,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "deviated, from the right way in speech."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Yz, O, K.) ―         -b3-  See also 4.       -A2-  It is also trans.: (O, TA:) you say,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "zAg qalobahu", "text_ar": "زاغ قَلْبَهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (O, K, * TA,) aor."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "yazuwgu", "text_ar": "يَزُوغُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (O, TA,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He made his heart to decline, deviate, swerve,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "turn aside."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(O, K, * TA.)"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "rab~anaA laA tazugo quluwbanaA", "text_ar": "رَبَّنَا لَا تَزُغْ قُلُوبَنَا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", with fet-h to the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "t", "text_ar": "ت"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and damm to the"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "z", "text_ar": "ز"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "O our Lord, make not our hearts to decline from the right way,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "in the Kur iii. 6, commonly read"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "tuzigo", "text_ar": "تُزِغْ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (see 4 in art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "zyg", "text_ar": "زيغ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ",)] is an extr. reading of Náfi. (O, TA.) ―         -b2-  [Hence, app., if it be correct,]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "zAg Aln~aAqapa", "text_ar": "زاغ النَّاقَةَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (O, K,) aor."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "yazuwgu", "text_ar": "يَزُوغُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "zawogN", "text_ar": "زَوْغٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (O,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He pulled the she-camel by the nose-rein:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(O, K:) so says Ibn- 'Abbád: but [Sgh says,] the verb in this sense is with the unpointed"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "E", "text_ar": "ع"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "only; which Ibn-'Abbád states to be the better known. (O, TA.)"}], "source_refs": ["IDrd", "O", "K", "TA", "Yz"]}, {"entry_id": "n18509", "headword_ar": "زَاغَ", "root": "zyg", "body": [{"kind": "text", "text": ", aor."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "yaziygu", "text_ar": "يَزِيغُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "zayogN", "text_ar": "زَيْغٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, O, Msb, K) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "zayagaAnN", "text_ar": "زَيَغَانٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "zayoguwgapN", "text_ar": "زَيْغُوغَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(O, K) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "zuyuwgN", "text_ar": "زُيُوغٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (TA,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "it,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(a thing, Msb,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "declined, deviated, swerved,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "turned aside,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, O, Msb, K,) from the right course or direction, accord. to an explanation of"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "zayogN", "text_ar": "زَيْغٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "by Er-Rághib; and from the truth: (TA:) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "zAg", "text_ar": "زاغ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", aor."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "yazuwgu", "text_ar": "يَزُوغُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "zawogN", "text_ar": "زَوْغٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", is a dial. var. thereof. (Msb, TA. *) In the Kur iii. 5, (O,)"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "zayogN", "text_ar": "زَيْغٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "means"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A doubting,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a declining,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "deviating, from the truth."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(O, K.) ―         -b2-  You say also,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "zaAgati Al$~amosu", "text_ar": "زَاغَتِ الشَّمْسُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (S, Msb, K,) aor."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "taziygu", "text_ar": "تَزِيغُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "zayogN", "text_ar": "زَيْغٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Msb, TA) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "zuyuwgN", "text_ar": "زُيُوغٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (TA,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The sun declined"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "from the meridian"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "], (S, * Msb, K,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "so that the shade turned from one side to the other."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, * K.) ―         -b3-  And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "zAg AlbaSaru", "text_ar": "زاغ البَصَرُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (S, O, K,) inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": 